<TITLE> Fitra Tk 40 in Dhaka, adjacent areas </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Sept 8 (bdnews24.com)  Authorities on Tuesday fixed Tk40 per head as fitra this year. The amount was fixed at a meeting at Islamic Foundation, said a press release Tuesday. Tk40 is applicable to Dhaka and adjacent areas taking into account the market price of rice and atta (coarse flour), while fitra in other parts will be fixed in line with market prices of rice and atta in the respective areas. Baitul Mokarram mosque's Khatib Moulana Mohammad Salahuddin chaired the meeting. In Islamic system, paying fitra is established to help poor people
